summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5729 for improvement of The Alley between 5th Avenue West and 6th Avenue West, from West Howe Street to West Crockett Street and certain other alleys, by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 75693, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
